icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Colorado River Management Plan</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1939286\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<a href=\"/grca/parkmgmt/upload/CRMPIF_s.pdf\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/management/images/201807ColoradoRiver_0374-Edit-2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Park rangers camp along the Colorado River while conducting a river patrol.\" src=\"/grca/learn/management/images/201807ColoradoRiver_0374-Edit-2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"201807ColoradoRiver_0374-Edit-2\"/>\n</picture>\n</a>\n<figcaption>Park rangers camp along the Colorado River while conducting a river patrol. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo.</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p><a href=\"/grca/learn/management/upload/CRMPIF_s.pdf\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1940715|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">The 2006 Colorado River Management Plan</a> is a visitor use management plan that specifies actions to conserve park resources and visitor experience while enhancing river running recreational opportunities on the Colorado River through Grand Canyon National Park.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1939852\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1939852\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<a href=\"/grca/parkmgmt/upload/Appendix A.pdf\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/management/images/River-with-flowers.JPG?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Flowers in the foreground with a river and canyon walls seen behind them.\" src=\"/grca/learn/management/images/River-with-flowers.JPG?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"River with flowers\"/>\n</picture>\n</a>\n<figcaption>A park ranger takes a photograph near the top of Hance Rapid, where Red Canyon meets the Colorado River, while conducting a backcountry patrol. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo.</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>The <a href=\"/grca/learn/management/upload/CRMP_ROD_2006.pdf\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1939899|\">Record of Decision</a> for the Final Environmental Impact Statement/Colorado River Management Plan for Grand Canyon National Park.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1939820\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1939820\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>A complete archive of Colorado River Management Plan documents is available at the park <a href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/muscol.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1960671,muscol.htm,14076|\">Museum Collection</a>.<br/>\n<br/>\nLearn more about the <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/management/crmp07rmm.htm\">Colorado River Management Research, Monitoring and Mitigation Program</a> or view the <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/management/crmp_rec_launch_archive.htm\">Recreational Launch Calendar</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: October 12, 2022</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
